      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "一、项目基本信息",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "黑体"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "1.项目名称：",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "2.项目地点：",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "3.勘探范围：",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "4.勘探期限：自         年          月          日至          年          月         日",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "二、甲方责任",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "黑体"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "1.甲方应向乙方提供项目相关的资料及用地的规划图纸、详细数据，并对其真实性和准确性负责，确保项目开展的合规性，为乙方的考古勘探工作提供必要的基础条件。保证在乙方进场前，完成地表的清障工作，如遇阻拦勘探工作等情况，甲方需解决协调无法勘探的问题，确保乙方勘探的正常有效进行，并提供工程场地内地下设施(包括电缆、光缆、天燃气管道及煤气管道等)的走向、深度、宽度及确切位置，以确保地下设施和工作人员的安全。未按协议约定提供有关资料、数据和工作条件，导致乙方无法按协议约定完成工作任务，甲方承担逾期责任。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "2.甲方有权对乙方的考古勘探工作进行监督，督促乙方履行文物保护责任，如发现乙方存在违反文物保护规定的行为，应及时向丙方报告。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "3.甲方应配合乙方和丙方开展文物保护相关工作，提供必要的协助和支持。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "4.甲方应对发现的古代文化遗存的现场安全与保密工作。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "三、乙方责任",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "黑体"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "1.乙方作为项目实施主体，对考古勘探过程中的文物安全负主要责任，须严格遵守国家及地方有关文物保护的法律法规和相关规定。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "2.乙方应建立健全文物保护管理制度，配备专门的文物保护人员，对参与勘探的工作人员进行文物保护知识和技能培训，确保工作人员具备相应的文物保护意识和能力。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "3.勘探过程中，乙方若发现文物遗迹，必须立即停止作业，在发现地点设置明显的警示标识，划定保护范围，采取有效的保护措施，防止文物受到损坏或遗失。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "4.发现文物遗迹后，乙方应在第一时间向丙方报告，报告内容应包括发现文物的时间、地点、数量、特征等详细信息，不得隐瞒不报或拖延报告。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "5.乙方需将文物遗迹的发现情况如实、详细地纳入考古勘探报告，确保报告的真实性和完整性。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "6.在丙方到达现场并作出处理意见前，乙方应负责现场的安全保卫工作，禁止任何单位和个人擅自进入保护范围或对文物进行处理。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "7.如发生文物损坏、遗失等情况，乙方应立即采取应急措施，并向甲、丙双方报告，配合相关部门进行调查处理，承担相应的责任。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
