      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "四、丙方责任",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "黑体"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "1.丙方负责对本区域内的文物保护工作进行监督和管理，指导乙方开展文物保护相关工作，向乙方和甲方宣传文物保护法律法规和政策。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "2.丙方在接到乙方关于发现文物遗迹的报告后，应及时组织专业人员赶赴现场，对文物遗迹进行勘查、鉴定和处理，指导乙方做好文物保护工作。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "3.丙方有权对乙方的考古勘探工作和文物保护措施进行检查，如发现问题，应责令乙方限期整改，确保文物安全。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "4.丙方应建立文物应急处置机制，在发生文物安全突发事件时，及时组织协调相关部门进行处置。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "五、责任追究",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "黑体"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "1.若因甲方未履行本责任书规定的责任，导致文物受到损坏或影响文物保护工作开展的，甲方应承担相应的责任。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "2.若乙方违反木责任书的规定，存在隐瞒不报、擅自处理文物遗迹、未按要求保护文物等行为，导致文物损坏、遗失或造成其他不良后果的，乙方应承担全部责任，赔偿由此造成的损失，并接受相关部门的处罚；情节严重的，依法追究法律责任。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "3.若因丙方未履行监督管理职责或处置不及时，导致文物受到损坏的，丙方应承担相应的责任。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "六、其他事项",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.2,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "黑体"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "1.本责任书自三方签字盖章之日起生效，有效期至项目考古勘探工作完成且文物处理完毕之目止。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "2.本责任书未尽事宜，由三方另行协商解决，可签订补充协议，补充协议与本责任书具有同等法律效力。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "3.本责任书一式三份，甲、乙、丙各执一份，具有同等法律效力。",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
      "left_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "right_indent_pt": 0.0,
      "space_before_pt": null,
      "space_after_pt": null,
      "line_spacing": "355600",
      "fonts": [
        "Times New Roman"
      ],
      "has_bold": false,
      "has_highlight": false
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "",
      "style": "Body Text",
      "alignment": "inherit",
      "first_line_indent_pt": 30.6,
